rows.label: tlk43100246_02_msg0001
rows.name: Thanks for the Nopon Chess Set!

rows.label: tlk43100246_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Whenever I'm at home,
I'm always playing it with that
mate I told you about.

rows.label: tlk43100246_02_msg0003
rows.name:
It's pretty well made. I bet it'll last a
lifetime.

rows.label: tlk43100246_02_msg0004
rows.name:
My mate's really smart though.
So I really gotta think about my
tactics!

rows.label: tlk43100246_02_msg0005
rows.name:
I gotta do my best to win. I feel like I'd
be letting him down as a friend if I
didn't!
